We as the car wash do not benefit one penny from this process and you as the customer does no t lose one penny... It's simply the way the banking process works. We have signs In all wash bays explaining this.

We as the car wash do not benefit one penny from this process and you as the customer does no t lose one penny... It's simply the way the banking process works. We have signs In all wash bays explaining this.

We as the car wash do not benefit one penny from this process and you as the customer does n ot lose one penny... It's simply the way the banking process works. We have signs In all wash bays explaining this.
